data.description: Welcome to your new home at 2969 Chamberlain Rd in Fairlawn! This exceptional ranch has great curb appeal. Walk into the foyer and then enter into the hardwood hall which has a formal dining room and a huge living room on either side!(Both rooms have hardwood)  The living room is 21 x 12 and has loads of windows and a gorgeous FP. Some rooms on the main level have been tastefully painted! There is a bonus room that a has a new door just installed that leads to a private flat backyard. The eat-in-kitchen flows to the dining rm or the 1st floor laundry room. There are 3 bedrooms, a main bath off of the hall and the master has it's own private full bath. The master bath has been recently remodeled with tile floors and a beautiful walk-in shower. Bedroom 1 has a walk-in closet! Tons of storage in this home. The basement has a finished 33x 14 rec room with a FP. There is also a full bath in the lower level. Tons of storage down here! Call for your private tour today!
